cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "StratAgent: An AI Management-Consulting Platform"
message: "If you use StratAgent in your research, please cite it."
type: software
authors:
  - family-names: Darpan
    email: darpan20071992@gmail.com
version: 0.1.0-rc2
date-released: "2026-07-10"
license: MIT
abstract: >-
  StratAgent is an AI management-consulting platform, packaged as a Claude Code
  plugin built on the Ruflo harness. It runs a full, governed consulting
  engagement on a business problem — classify, scope, frame, analyze, review,
  challenge, validate, and report — enforcing evidence traceability and a
  mandatory Reviewer and Challenger governance pass before any report is
  produced. Independent evaluation found its governance layer measurably catches
  overconfidence and blind spots relative to a single-pass baseline.
keywords:
  - management-consulting
  - multi-agent-systems
  - llm-agents
  - governance
  - ai-evaluation
  - claude-code
